  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u00a0 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Defeat Dictatorship and Make Democracy Win - Sajid",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Take to the streets tomorrow. Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa has called upon the people of the country to defeat dictatorship and make democracy win.",
        "A police curfew has been imposed as people prepare for a massive protest against the government tomorrow.",
        "Police have been enforced in Colombo North, Colombo South, Colombo Madhi, Nukegoda, Kelani, Negombo Police Divisions from 9pm tonight until further notice.",
        "In this case, the police curfew is a fraud. It is illegal. Take to the streets tomorrow. Defeat dictatorship and make democracy triumph. Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa has called the people that we can do it."
      ],
